AUDIO: 'When I\'ve seen patients when they\'ve gotten&nbsp; BCIs and it takes a couple days configuring it,&nbsp;&nbsp; was it similar for you the first time you put&nbsp; that on? Did it take a minute to Oddly enough, no.&nbsp;&nbsp; I think I\'ve probably had gestures working in like&nbsp; 10 minutes. Um, it\'s designed to be really simple.&nbsp;&nbsp;'

